# рџЏ† HolyClub Esports Analytics

A data analytics project built on top of a real-world esports platform database.

This project explores competitive matchmaking, player performance, championships, platform operations and community behavior using SQL, Python, MySQL and Business Intelligence concepts.

The goal is to transform raw operational data into actionable insights, KPIs and dashboards that support strategic decision-making within the HolyClub ecosystem.

---

## рџЋ® About HolyClub

HolyClub is a competitive Counter-Strike 2 platform that provides:

* Competitive Matchmaking
* Championships and Tournaments
* Player Rankings and ELO System
* HolyCoins Economy
* Community Features
* Support and Moderation Systems
* Anti-Cheat and Fair Play Monitoring

This project leverages real production data to perform analytical exploration and generate business insights.

